snippet.title: PSX Longplay [111] PowerSlave
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played By: ScHlAuChi

Known in Europe as Exhumed, this is probably THE best PSX FPS game with great gameplay and graphics! All secrets and both endings are shown! -
